rows.label: tlk45350171_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I've finished selling all the goods
I brought from Superbia, so I'm off
to the cathedral for a spot of prayer.

rows.label: tlk45350171_01_msg0002
rows.name:
No, I'm not particularly religious or
anything. I just want to get a glimpse of
Fan-sama, Goddess of the Holy See!

rows.label: tlk45350171_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There are Invidians in this city too,
but when I gaze at Fan-sama, all that
political unrest seems so insignificant.
